ong>). They will then be particularly tender.","The chicken skewers can also be grilled in the oven at 200°C until golden brown.","The skewers and satay sauce can be served hot or cold.","<strong>Spicy peanut satay sauce:<\/strong> Add ½ tsp cayenne pepper during the final step.","Try using pork or turkey instead of chicken."],"basicInfo":["medium","40m","2h","30 pieces"]}